text: Auteuil may refer to: ==Places== * Auteuil, Oise, a commune in France * Auteuil, Quebec, a former city that is now a district within Laval, Quebec, Canada * Auteuil, Yvelines, a commune in France * Neuilly-Auteuil-Passy, an area of Paris * Auteuil Hippodrome, a racecourse in west Paris ==People== * Aurore Auteuil (born 1981), French actress * Daniel Auteuil (born 1950), French actor ==Paris Métro stations== * Église d'Auteuil (Paris Métro) * Michel-Ange – Auteuil (Paris Métro) * Porte d'Auteuil (Paris Métro) ==See also== * Autheuil (disambiguation)
title: Auteuil
